OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772351614
OL,3,CStarmer warns Iran not to attack UK
OL,4,Cmilitary in Middle East
OL,6,FThe UK government's statement on the
OL,7,FUS and Israeli attack on Iran faces in
OL,8,Fboth directions, as usual.
OL,10,FOn the one hand, it says the UK
OL,11,Fmilitary is not participating - which
OL,12,Fis unsurprising, given that it is
OL,13,Fdifficult to make a case for the
OL,14,Fattack under international law.
OL,16,FOn the other, it says that Iran must
OL,17,Fnot develop nuclear weapons (the first
OL,18,Fsentence) and there is no criticism of
OL,19,FTrump or Netanyahu for launching the
OL,20,Fstrikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
