PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772351614
OL,3,CStarmer warns Iran not to attack UK
OL,4,Cmilitary in Middle East
OL,6,FThere is however a warning to Tehran
OL,7,Fnot to attack UK military assets and
OL,8,Fpersonnel in the Middle East.
OL,10,F"We stand ready to protect our
OL,11,Finterests," says the statement - which
OL,12,Fcarries the implication that the UK
OL,13,Fmay yet find itself in armed conflict
OL,14,Fwith Iran.
OL,16,FThe PM is due to chair a Cobr meeting
OL,17,Fof relevant ministers, military
OL,18,Fleaders and intelligence specialists
OL,19,Flater this morning.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@KO]
